s&quot;, they did not have a coffee maker or fridge... and remember...it is a casino...so if you are not &quot;playing&quot; you are &quot;paying&quot; for drinks, coffee, and even soda. The deluxe rooms now have a fridge and etc. I would recommend this place to others and would stay here agian.	
